txt.en: 'I'm afraid not, thank you for asking. I promise to let you know if I hear anything.'
'Has there been any word from Merry, Saradoc?'
'Did you bake up any special treats today?'
'I can always make up something special for you, my dear. I'll have some tarts delivered this evening.'
'Has there been any word from Merry, Saradoc?'
